      "amount": "1 tbsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "olive oil",
      "amount": "2 tbsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a Dutch oven over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, diced celery, smoked paprika, cayenne pepper, and salt, cooking for 2 minutes.",
    "Add lentils, water, and vegetable broth, bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low.",
    "Cover and simmer for 25 minutes, stirring occasionally, until lentils are tender but al dente.",
    "Stir in maple syrup and soy sauce, then simmer for another 3 minutes to develop a glassy glaze.",
    "Remove from heat, let rest 5 minutes, then serve warm."
